     <TD BGCOLOR="#f7f5e6"><TEXTAREA NAME="message" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">/agree on waiting until you get track.

I thought I would never see any zone again when hunting for that skin.  Not only did I /auc for it, I hired younger trolls and ogres to hunt the gators for em (was 20smthg when i did the quest I think) and PL'd em as they hunted.  Would make myself go to zone and either a) kill 5 of the right gators (even with track that can take awhile) or b) stay and hunt them for a certain period of time.  I also offered to pay to have trolls go check all the vendors in their town to see if a skin happened to be in the vendor inventory.  And I checked Slaggak all the time since I could get to him and he was right near where the piece would have dropped.

It was a miserable experience, though I suppose since the item is really very good for a quest you can do in your teens, they can't make it too easy.

Eventually picked it up from a character via auction but tried lots of different approaches.  You may want to do the same.</TEXTAREA></TD>
